##The average woman buys a fake mask

Micro-signal, zxmtnx

Features, women's power, flowing like water. New Media Women, women's Rights Watch. CONTACT E-MAIL: gzxmtnx@163. Weibo:@new media women@i have experienced sexism

Lead language: The new crown pneumonia epidemic prevention war advancement affects all people's hearts, 2020 this year may be said to be thrilling. Chinese New Year does not visit, do not shop, holiday from January 31 to February 3 to February 10, every day we busy receive a large number of information, proof, forward appeal, contact mutual assistance, i believe everyone has had the most unforgettable Spring Festival holiday in their lives.

In the midst of an explosion of information and heartbreaking stories every day, we feel we have to write journalistically to help digest our own emotions. On every Weibo and facebook page, in the middle of the night, angry, sad, anxious and unable to sleep because of 24 hour progress, we try to record the present moment in bits and pieces.

We think that these words are also important. I'm afraid we've all learned the importance of recording and sharing these days. So from now on, new media women started the "ordinary women epidemic record" column, to receive all about the personal epidemic story submission. Today we share a diary from watermelon, she is in Guangzhou, because she bought a fake mask, now I do not know how to protect myself in the air conditioning office building after the holiday..

By watermelons

Editor / Park Sai

Debutantenew media women

A Bolt from the Blue

I'm so mad. I got a mask.

The mask was bought by my father at my insistence on January 23, the day Wuhan was closed. Back then, the small-town pharmacy had a few in stock. But according to my father said he went to buy when the door is pouring into a large crowd, presumably heard the news of the city closed in Wuhan, my father quickly asked the clerk to get him two boxes.

However, on the morning of February 3, I saw someone forwarded the article "exposure! These domestic and foreign masks are all fake! Please forward to remind everyone! " To reveal which are fake masks. I looked, my God, the two boxes that dad bought for us were on the list. I told my brother the news at once, and everyone's heart sank. I tried to cut off one of the masks and found that although it was a three-layer mask, the material was thin and you could see it with your fingers down the bottom. This mask is much thinner than other medical masks and another Japanese mask. The aperture of the mask is probably too big to stop the foam.

(fake face mask to chill my heart)

How to work without a mask

I was counting on these 50 masks to go to work, and now I don't have any at all. I feel anxious. For example, if you go to a quiet place or an empty place, you can hang it on the balcony for a few hours and reuse it, experts say. For example, wear two more layers. All kinds of information is difficult to distinguish true and false, dizzy but anxious... and brother comfort each other, brother said, is better than not wear. Micro-blog media interviews with various experts also said that as long as the mask is useful. My brother and I tacitly did not tell the parents in the hometown let them worry. They don't have any extra masks.

These days have seen a number of popular science, I basically do not worry about outdoor protection, false mask is barely used. My concern is that I'll have to take the subway to work later, and that kind of crowded space is bound to be fortified. I don't know how many people get masks that are just as fake as mine, and can't even buy one.

Guangzhou can now every night at 8:00, through the Sui Kang Small Procedure to reserve five masks. But robbed for three days, also failed to grab, but still have to continue to rob every day, or what can be done (booth hands) . I asked my friend Egypt (?) To buy some masks for me, but I don't know when I will get them.

When I went downstairs to buy vegetables on Feb. 3, I saw a notice at the entrance of the market saying that you must wear a mask to enter the market. I went in and found that, compared to the fifth day of the year, there was only one vegetable seller and one meat seller. That day, there were already two meat sellers and several vegetable sellers. After buying vegetables, I wanted to buy some beef balls. So I went to the butcher's. After I got closer, I found that the butcher didn't wear a mask! But always thin-skinned very afraid of embarrassment I am ashamed not to buy, so hard to buy and he bought half a catty of beef balls. Then I realized that he probably couldn't buy a mask either, and I understood a little more.

A poor cover makes me feel sad

On the morning of February 4, when I saw the article on the occasion of which the masks should be used, I couldn't help feeling a little angry. Where does that come from now? . You can't buy a mask now. . Went to all the forums, social media groups, and everyone was wearing fake masks. Even the fake is not too willing to use, let me have a kind of bittersweet sense of humor.

Although I have been washed my hands frequently by science popularization before, it is much more important than wearing a mask, but still a few voices. On the 4th, this kind of science popularization finally became more and more. I don't know if it is because everyone can not buy a mask, go downstairs to pick up the express to buy vegetables with the mask back and go out with the clothes hanging in the sun, as the scene looks a bit bleak, I took a picture to save.

(it's kind of sad)

I also remember the last few days do not know where to see the science or can be used to alcohol sterilization mask, so that day I used mask spray alcohol and then dry again. The New Popular Science Review on the 4th has denied this practice, reminding everyone to only dry, can not use any other disinfectant spray one-time mask. There are also many funny pictures on the Internet about the mask disinfection, we continue to make merry in misery.

(Internet users laugh in their misery)

Kopp says wearing a mask isn't as important as it sounds, but the lack of masks on my hands still makes me anxious. Especially when the office building is air conditioning and the windows don't open, which makes me feel like I have to wear a mask all the time. In my anxiety, I studied the practicality of buying a cotton mask + Labor insurance and replacing it with KN95 / KN90 filter..

These days, when I'm talking to my friends, there's always a mask. Not only do we need masks for ourselves, we need masks for our families, and we need to worry about doctors and nurses on the front line not having masks and protective clothing and goggles. When will the days of worrying about masks end?
